---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import TopStrip from '../components/TopStrip.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title="關於 Gobaligo — 峇里島旅遊中文攻略網站"
      description="Gobaligo 是一個專門寫給華語旅客的峇里島旅遊指南，超過 610 篇實地體驗文章，涵蓋景點、住宿、交通、美食、簽證、行程規劃工具等。"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <TopStrip lang="zh-tw" />

    <main class="about-page">

      <section class="about-hero">
        <div class="about-hero-inner">
          <div class="about-logo">🌴</div>
          <h1>關於 Gobaligo</h1>
          <p class="about-tagline">峇里島旅遊中文攻略，一站搞定你的整趟行程</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>這個網站是什麼？</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Gobaligo（gobaligo.id）</strong> 是一個專門為<strong>說中文的旅客</strong>打造的峇里島旅遊指南。
          我們用繁體中文（同時提供簡體中文、英文版）寫出超過 <strong>610 篇</strong>實地採訪與親身體驗的文章，
          涵蓋景點、住宿評測、餐廳美食、包車司機、簽證通關、行程規劃等各種你需要知道的資訊。
        </p>
        <p>
          我們不是旅行社，也沒有業配包裝，每一篇文章都是真實走過、用過、吃過才寫的。
          如果你在網路上查峇里島中文資料查到頭痛，那這裡就是你需要的地方。
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>我們能幫你什麼？</h2>
        <div class="about-features">
          <div class="about-feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🗺️</span>
            <h3>分區攻略</h3>
            <p>烏布、庫塔、水明漾、努沙杜瓦、金巴蘭、沙努爾⋯各區特色、必去景點與怎麼移動，全部整理好了。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🏨</span>
            <h3>住宿推薦</h3>
            <p>從百元民宿到頂級別墅，幫你篩選真正值得住的選項，附上位置、設施與訂房連結。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🚗</span>
            <h3>包車 & 叫車</h3>
            <p>峇里島沒有計程車文化，我們整理了包車司機推薦名單、Grab 叫車教學、機場接送行情，讓你不被坑。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🍜</span>
            <h3>美食餐廳</h3>
            <p>從路邊 Warung 到高空餐廳，我們親自吃過，幫你找出每個區域真正好吃又不踩雷的選擇。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">📋</span>
            <h3>簽證 & 通關</h3>
            <p>印尼落地簽、VOA 線上申請、海關注意事項，最新版規定一次看懂。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🧰</span>
            <h3>旅遊工具</h3>
            <p>行程規劃工具、預算計算器、景點門票費用表、即時天氣、互動地圖，出發前必用。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section about-stats">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">610+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">篇旅遊文章</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">4</span>
          <span class="stat-label">種語言版本</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">2019</span>
          <span class="stat-label">年開始寫</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>找到我們</h2>
        <p>有問題、想合作，或是你有峇里島資訊想分享，歡迎透過以下管道聯繫我們：</p>
        <div class="about-social">
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@j_indonesia" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-btn social-yt">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20"><path d="M23.498 6.186a3.016 3.016 0 0 0-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.017 3.017 0 0 0 .502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.016 3.016 0 0 0 2.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.015 3.015 0 0 0 2.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814zM9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12l-6.273 3.568z"/></svg>
            YouTube @j_indonesia
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/bali.guide.blog" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-btn social-fb">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20"><path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/></svg>
            Facebook 粉絲團
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section about-cta">
        <h2>準備好出發了嗎？</h2>
        <p>不知道從哪裡開始？先去看看我們為新手整理的完整入門攻略吧！</p>
        <div class="cta-btns">
          <a href="/blog/?lang=tw&cat=新手指南" class="cta-btn cta-primary">📖 新手入門指南</a>
          <a href="/trip-planner/" class="cta-btn cta-secondary">🗓️ 開始規劃行程</a>
        </div>
      </section>

    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
.about-page {
  max-width: 860px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 1.5em 4em;
}

.about-hero {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 3.5em 1em 2.5em;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ocean, #1A365D) 0%, #2a5298 100%);
  margin: 0 -1.5em 2.5em;
  color: #fff;
}

.about-hero-inner { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }

.about-logo {
  font-size: 3.5em;
  margin-bottom: 0.3em;
  line-height: 1;
}

.about-hero h1 {
  font-size: 2em;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin: 0 0 0.4em;
  color: #fff;
}

.about-tagline {
  font-size: 1.05em;
  opacity: 0.88;
  margin: 0;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.about-section {
  margin-bottom: 3em;
}

.about-section h2 {
  font-size: 1.25em;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--ocean, #1A365D);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--gold, #C9A84C);
  padding-left: 0.7em;
  margin: 0 0 1em;
}

.about-section p {
  font-size: 1em;
  line-height: 1.85;
  color: var(--text, #333);
  margin: 0 0 1em;
}

/* Feature cards */
.about-features {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1.2em;
  margin-top: 1.2em;
}

.about-feature-card {
  background: #faf8f4;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.25);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 1.2em 1em;
}

.feature-icon {
  font-size: 1.8em;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 0.4em;
}

.about-feature-card h3 {
  font-size: 0.95em;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--ocean, #1A365D);
  margin: 0 0 0.4em;
}

.about-feature-card p {
  font-size: 0.85em;
  line-height: 1.65;
  color: #555;
  margin: 0;
}

/* Stats */
.about-stats {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 2em;
  background: var(--ocean, #1A365D);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 2em;
  margin-bottom: 3em;
}

.stat-item {
  text-align: center;
  color: #fff;
}

.stat-number {
  display: block;
  font-size: 2.2em;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--gold, #C9A84C);
  line-height: 1;
}

.stat-label {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.85em;
  opacity: 0.8;
  margin-top: 0.3em;
}

.stat-divider {
  width: 1px;
  height: 50px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
}

/* Social */
.about-social {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1em;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: 1.2em;
}

.social-btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5em;
  padding: 0.6em 1.2em;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: 0.9em;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: opacity 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
}

.social-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; transform: translateY(-1px); }

.social-yt {
  background: #FF0000;
  color: #fff;
}

.social-fb {
  background: #1877F2;
  color: #fff;
}

/* CTA */
.about-cta {
  background: #faf8f4;
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 2em;
  text-align: center;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.25);
}

.about-cta h2 {
  border-left: none;
  padding-left: 0;
  text-align: center;
}

.cta-btns {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1em;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: 1.2em;
}

.cta-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 0.7em 1.5em;
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-size: 0.95em;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
}

.cta-btn:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.12);
}

.cta-primary {
  background: var(--gold, #C9A84C);
  color: var(--ocean, #1A365D);
}

.cta-secondary {
  background: var(--ocean, #1A365D);
  color: #fff;
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .about-hero h1 { font-size: 1.5em; }
  .about-features { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .about-stats { gap: 1.2em; padding: 1.5em; }
  .stat-number { font-size: 1.7em; }
}

@media (max-width: 420px) {
  .about-features { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .about-stats { flex-direction: column; gap: 1em; }
  .stat-divider { width: 50px; height: 1px; }
}
</style>
